 Release Notes                                                                 
                                                                               
 Itchy Vibes is a one-man project founded in 2006 by Swedish producer          
 Christian Larsson, who started his musical career as a local dj.              
 The interest in electronic music grew, and he started to compose techno using 
 a dos based sequencer called \"Impulse Tracker\". As time went by, more and  more
 advanced software became the standard.                                        
                                                                               
 The progress of creating an original sound varied a lot in style, often       
 crossing the border to other genres and styles, but Itchy Vibes finally       
 settled in the melodic \"Full On\" side of Psytrance, inspired by artists such  
 as Astrix, Eskimo, GMS, Son Kite, and Hux Flux, as well as a heavy influence  
 from other parts of the Scandinavian Psytrance and Techno scene.
